com.fincons.rabbitmq.subscriber
Interface Subscriber

All Superinterfaces:
RabbitMqClient
All Known Implementing Classes:
BasicSubscriber
public interface Subscriber
extends RabbitMqClient

This interface models a consumer of a specific set of events dispatched by another RabbitMQ Server client.
The actual processing of the events is performed by the registered instances of EventListener: the method EventListener#onEvent(ENSEvent) is called every time a new event has been received by the subscriber.

Author:
Fincons Group AG
